'''Sovar''' lived on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] and acted as a cargo solicitor for the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]]. On one run, he was only able to secure a cargo of nearly worthless [[glaze cake]]s, and so bought her a drink at a local [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] to compensate. While there, [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] tried to capture Okeefe, but she successfully escaped.

